OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,FChannel Islanders have shared their
OL,7,Fthoughts on the death of Pope Francis,
OL,8,Fdescribing him as a "much-loved" and
OL,9,F"true shepherd" of the people.
OL,11,FPope Francis died aged 88 on Monday
OL,12,Fmorning (21 April); he was last seen
OL,13,Faddressing the Easter Sunday mass in
OL,14,FSt Peter's Square.
OL,16,FThe Vatican said in a statement: "At
OL,17,F7:35 this morning (local time), the
OL,18,FBishop of Rome, Francis, returned to
OL,19,Fthe house of the Father. His entire
OL,20,Flife was dedicated to the service of
OL,21,Fthe Lord and His Church."
