OL,6,FHe explains: "That comes about in the
OL,7,Fway he wanted to live, when he
OL,8,Fdeclined to use the papal apartments
OL,9,Fand instead lived in the hotel next
OL,10,Fdoor.
OL,12,F"Pope Francis was a good, true
OL,13,Fshepherd who had a great love and
OL,14,Fconcern for the poor and the
OL,15,Fmarginalised."
OL,17,FRev. Canon Rutledge recalls being
OL,18,Fmoved by the Pope's message to priests
OL,19,Fto be "shepherds with 'the smell of
OL,20,Fthe sheep'"
