OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,FThe Guernsey Dean adds: "As clergy, we
OL,7,Fshould be there with our people and
OL,8,Fnot be sitting in offices - to be a
OL,9,Ftrue shepherd just like Jesus was.
OL,11,F"That very much grew on me."
OL,13,FCatholic Dean of Jersey, the Very
OL,14,FReverand Dominic Golding, told ITV
OL,15,FNews that Pope Francis was a leader
OL,16,Fwho spoke up on the most important
OL,17,Fvalues Christians should strive for in
OL,18,Fsociety.
