OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,FHe explains: "We are mourning a man
OL,7,Fwho's certainly been much-loved and a
OL,8,Fman who I think showed great
OL,9,Fcompassion for others.
OL,11,F"Particularly for him, he was very
OL,12,Fkeen to minister not only to those in
OL,13,Fthe Catholic Church, but to all those
OL,14,Fhe memorably said are on the
OL,15,Fperipheries of the church and society.
