OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,F"Especially for his work with
OL,7,Fmigrants, refugees, the elderly, the
OL,8,Fsick, and for example, the Christian
OL,9,FCommunity in Gaza, whom he's phoned
OL,10,Fevery Sunday evening until just the
OL,11,Flast few weeks to assure them that
OL,12,Fthey weren't forgotten.
OL,14,F"I think for people of faith and for
OL,15,Fpeople who have good will to others,
OL,16,Fhe's someone whom they can all
OL,17,Fidentify with - many of us are very
OL,18,Fproud of what he's achieved."
