OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,FPatrick Lynch, CEO of Caritas, which
OL,7,Freaches out to the marginalised in our
OL,8,Fsociety, says Pope Francis will be
OL,9,Fremembered as someone who taught the
OL,10,Fchurch to take action for those most
OL,11,Fvulnerable in society.
OL,13,F"I think he was a wonderful Pope. He
OL,14,Fchanged the way the papacy did a lot
OL,15,Fof things. For us who work in Catholic
OL,16,Fsocial teaching and social justice, he
OL,17,Fwas an amazing leader.
