OL,3,CChannel Island Catholic leaders react
OL,4,Cto Pope Francis' death
OL,6,F"He inspired through his actions and
OL,7,Fhis words - he was somebody who always
OL,8,Fhad time and worked for the poor and
OL,9,Fthe voiceless and the downtrodden.
OL,11,F"There's that famous photograph of him
OL,12,Ftravelling on the bus when he gave up
OL,13,Fthe chauffeur for his limousine
OL,14,Fbecause he wanted to be a person for
OL,15,Fthe people."
